{{redirect|Pedro Cabral|the Portuguese rugby union player|Pedro Cabral (rugby union)}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2013}}
{{Use American English|date=July 2017}}
{{Infobox person
| image       = Pedro Alvares Cabral.jpg{{!}}border
| alt         = Half-length painted portrait of a bearded man wearing a hat with a large feather.
| occupation  = Fleet commander for [[Kingdom of Portugal|Portugal]]
| caption     = A 32- to 33-year old Pedro Álvares Cabral in an early 20th-century painting. No contemporary portraits of Cabral are known to exist.{{sfn|Bueno|1998|p=35}}
